rComments: Great prof!  Limited by how far he could deviate from the textbook due to all first year psych classes being standardized, but made things crystal clear and provided interesting videos.  Read the textbook and you'll definitely pass!
Great prof!  Very funny and makes content interesting and very approachable.  I wish he had more classes.
definitely my favourite prof this semester, he makes the content very interesting and hes super organized. all his powerpoints cover the class completely. its easy to do well if you study

Professor Burr is a young prof who lectures clearly and is interesting to listen to. He uses videos and clear powerpoint slides during lectures which are easy to follow and take notes. Ppts and related material are posted on VC. The textbook is a good read, and worth your money/time if taking this class. Myers online study guide also recommended.
Good prof, clear, and helpful, midterms are avrg, go to class and you'll do fine.
